  "title": "Fleming's Abduction, Part II",
  "summary": "Aboard the freighter Whipping Star, ISB Sector Director Korynn Fleming wakes immobilized to find that his abductors are Darth Malign and his old enemy Captain Dareus, both now serving the Emperor directly through a secret Sith organization. Enraged at first, Fleming recovers his interrogator's composure as Malign departs to meditate and Dareus, treating him with disarming respect, explains his redemption and the grand design of a new galactic order rooted in ancient secrets. Wary but pragmatic, Fleming chooses to keep an open mind and play along, reasoning that cooperation places him to act should the pair prove false. After a series of evasive hyperspace jumps, the ship arrives at the asteroid-hidden Star Destroyer Predator, where elite black-and-crimson droids and a rankless crew greet them. Dareus and Fleming exchange icy words about their shared past before Fleming reaffirms his absolute loyalty to the Emperor, and Dareus, letting bygones go, welcomes him as an honored guest and escorts the weary director to his stateroom.",
